nodes.text: A squad of clone troopers served within the 41st Elite Corps and was led by Jedi General Luminara Unduli and squad leader "Buzz." After Geonosian Archduke Poggle the Lesser went in hiding during the Second Battle of Geonosis, the squad was deployed to search for him. The two commanding officers of the squad, Unduli and Buzz, found the Progate Temple but were captured and Buzz was killed.
